# SkyWeb Change Log

## DN-9.4.1 — Alert Overlay Page Wiring Fix

- Restored page-level alert overlay loading for the .NET-lane indicator detail page.
- Restored page-level alert overlay loading for the .NET-lane macro-view detail page.
- Indicator charts now fetch matching authenticated alert rules, rule event history, and notification history before passing overlays into ChartPanel.
- Macro-view charts now fetch matching active view-metric alerts and filter overlays to selected chart series.
